# 天命项目根 .gitignore · 2026-06-17 建立版本控制基线
# 原则：源码与配置入库；依赖 / 产物 / 归档 / 临时 / 大媒体 / 敏感数据 一律排除。

# ── 依赖 ──
node_modules/
**/node_modules/

# ── 嵌套的烂尾 git 仓库（顶层接管后移走备份）──
web/.git/
web/.git-defunct*/

# ── 归档 / 临时 / scratch（不入版本控制）──
_archive/
dev-tools/
_asset-backups/
_codex_tmp/
_codex_release_*/
_codex_tmp_*
_pw-scratch/
_scratch_online/
_scratch_uiux/
.pushtmp/
.playwright-cli/
**/.playwright-cli/
__pycache__/
**/__pycache__/
*.pyc
stdout

# ── 构建 / 发布产物 ──
output/
**/output/
dist/
build/
**/dist/
**/build/
mobile/android/
mobile/ios/
mobile/.gradle/
**/*.zip
**/*.tm-pack
**/*.bin
release-hot/_release-*/
release-hot/downloads/
release-hot/files/
release-hot/manifests/
mobile/capgo-dist/
mobile/capgo/
*.apk
*.aab
.hot-update-manifest.json
web/.hot-update-manifest.json

# ── 大媒体 / 生成资源 / 独立工程（基线聚焦代码·媒体与 godot 另管）──
宣传片/
web/godot/
web/generated_images/
web/_screenshots/
web/test-results/
web/vendor/models/Xenova/
*.gif
*.png
*.jpg
*.jpeg
*.webp
*.bmp
*.ico
*.mp3
*.mp4
*.wav
*.webm
*.mov
*.ttf
*.otf
*.woff
*.woff2

# ── 备份文件（.bak 家族·本地保留不入库）──
*.bak
*.bak-*
*.bak*
*.backup-*

# ── 敏感：密钥 / 凭据 / 用户数据（绝不入库）──
*.key
*.pem
*.p12
.env
.env.*
secrets.json
**/.guoshi-live-config.json
**/.guoshi-live*.json
**/server-secret.key
**/*.sqlite
**/*.sqlite3
**/saves/
**/__autosave__.json
*_repro-save.json

# ── 日志 / IDE / OS ──
*.log
.vscode/
.idea/
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
desktop.ini
*.swp
*~
.claude/
_capsync_hold/
